A significant number of casualties are anticipated following a collision involving a train and a Bus Rapid Transit (BRT) vehicle in Ikeja Along area of Lagos. It was gathered that the BRT was conveying civil servants to the State Secretariat, Alausa, Ikeja when the sad incident occurred. The train collided with the BRT, causing it to be dragged from the Ikeja Along area to Shogunle. Several passengers are feared dead following the impact of the sad collision.